snippet.title: Sony Pictures Entertainment
snippet.description: Welcome to the official channel for Sony Pictures Entertainment. Subscribe now to get weekly first looks at our films, including the latest movie trailers, exclusive movie clips, and vignettes! Stay tuned for some behind the scenes moments and messages from your favorite actors!
